<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<title>Tic Tac Toe</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">

<style>
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto auto auto;
  grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
  grid-gap: 20px;
  background-color: #2196F3;
  padding: 20px;
}

.grid-container > div {
  background-color: #c1d9ff;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 0;
  font-size: 30px;
}

.button {
    background-color: #c1d9ff;
    border: 0;
    color: red;
    padding: auto;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 50px;
    cursor: pointer;
    
}

.active, .button:hover {
	background-color: red;
	color: white;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

	<!-- Audio is tacky, I know. However, it's about all I could get to work on this project, so... -->
<audio controls autoplay style="display:none">
  <source src="Shall-we-play-a-game.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<center>
	<h1>Tic Tac Toe (aka Noughts & Crosses)</h1>

<i>Click in a box to make your move.</i><br><br>




